      <title>消息称美联储放松银行资本计划面临监管机构阻力</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/feds-relaxed-bank-capital-plan-faces-fdic-pushback-bloomberg-news-reports-2024-09-20/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据三位知情人士透露，美联储具有里程碑意义的银行资本方案的淡化版本正面临最高银行监管机构联邦存款保险公司（FDIC）的抵制。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/feds-relaxed-bank-capital-plan-faces-fdic-pushback-bloomberg-news-reports-2024-09-20/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 20 Sep 2024 14:13:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国兴业银行首席执行官克鲁帕因银行扭亏为盈计划收紧成本</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/socgens-ceo-krupa-tightens-screws-costs-banks-turnaround-plan-falls-flat-2024-09-20/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国兴业银行首席执行官斯拉沃米尔·克鲁帕（Slawomir Krupa）准备进一步控制成本，继续推进一年前宣布的扭亏为盈战略，但该战略迄今未能提振这家法国银行低迷的股价。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/socgens-ceo-krupa-tightens-screws-costs-banks-turnaround-plan-falls-flat-2024-09-20/</guid>
